      "date": "2013-02-11 15:22:08.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI think most of the patch is ok, but I don't like the change to send an ostid from the MDS to the OSS during create. It would be better to just fix the OST validate code to allow an IDIF FID.",
