      "date": "2013-02-12 04:40:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/97a1a308-74cc-11e2-bf59-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
